snippet.title: Hamas Militants Raid Israeli Town

localized.description:
(Video strictly for news/educational purposes). 
Hamas terrorists have crossed from Gaza into the nearby Israeli town of Zikim. The Israeli air force and navy then work together to neutralize the threat. Over the past week the situation between Israel and Hamas has escalated. Israel now considers a ground operation in the Gaza Strip.
Video Attribution: Google Maps, Israel Defense Forces
